{"tid":1819381,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日會痴文宣既！有幾點要注意！","createTime":"2020-01-10T18:09:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T04:34:22.000Z","uid":22717,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3767032bf89041f8a6348ff697ab66d5e1e85caf","tid":1819381,"uid":22717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T18:09:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\">1.各大連儂牆必定會有便衣狗駐守</span><br />\n手足們<span style=\"color: red;\">快手貼完就好走</span> <br />\n唔好哂時間同人傾計鳩up<br />\n今晚叫到手足痴痴下同啲老人家吹水<br />\n聽日就盡量避免<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">2.必定會有藍絲引起事端</span><br />\n藍絲淨係嘈既就唔洗理 快手貼完快手走<br />\n郁手就幾個人禁住佢就即刻跑走<br />\n因為相信大部分人都唔會full bloc去貼<br />\n多數都街坊裝戴個口罩<br />\n咁樣郁手太易俾狗trace<br />\n加上一定有便衣防暴係附近<br />\n所以最好有事就走<br />\n記得聽日<span style=\"color: red;\">主要既目的係文宣</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">3.冇份貼都行過幫手睇水</span><br />\n唔洗同手足傾計講加油<br />\n幫手<span style=\"color: red;\">睇水就係最好既加油</span>"},{"pid":"d9a12c95be5ce4398548c595854b41f633237a1b","tid":1819381,"uid":22717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T18:10:09.000Z","msg":"中国肺炎"},{"pid":"88b1cdc8e714fa85472978ace78370145418117a","tid":1819381,"uid":22717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T18:10:19.000Z","msg":"中国肺炎"},{"pid":"136a9d98d82a8dcc4eb9a96fb5689aa73b6d9aa2","tid":1819381,"uid":22717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T18:10:33.000Z","msg":"中国肺炎"},{"pid":"407afec9a002f6e38b29608a8dece75d5aa28922","tid":1819381,"uid":22717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T18:10:44.000Z","msg":"中国肺炎"},{"pid":"fc6c6b7ff9d4d438d304aa609dc66701bf932fc2","tid":1819381,"uid":22717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T18:10:55.000Z","msg":"中国肺炎"},{"pid":"10d7dffaeff5c079e478b00037815b57a7daebfe","tid":1819381,"uid":22717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T18:11:07.000Z","msg":"中国肺炎"},{"pid":"367657a4896b47a